headline: See essential dive data at a glance with the Descent X30 large-format dive computer from Garmin
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) today announced Descent™ X30, an easy-to-read, large-format dive computer with an eco-friendly design. Featuring a vibrant 2.4-inch display and a housing and bezel made with recycled ocean-bound plastics, Descent X30 is ready for the next dive with large leakproof metal buttons, a 10 ATM dive rating and up to 30 hours of battery life. It also includes support for multiple dive profiles and new NDL Aware™ depth metrics to help divers explore for longer.
